[center][img]http://telarium.org/img/banner.gif[/img][/center]
Play now at http://telarium.org/play
Welcome and thank you for visiting our toplist page! Telarium is a brand new RSPS striving to become the most advanced RSPS out there. We offer an amazing experience for our players all around the world.
Telarium has something for everyone! Some of our features include:
Dedicated server + Website Amazing & improved combat system Custom minigames, some include Zombies, Weapon Master, and Infected Safe Pk Box Soul wars, Clan Wars, Castle Wars Custom Slayer (slayer master teleports you right to task!) Great slayer rewards An Abundance of bosses, some include, Nex, Nomad, Corp, and GWD Full Construction and Summoning All working skills Fair EXP Rates Fair item drops Unique players to train and monsters to kill! Unique player shops, filled with items to enjoy! Custom Home/Spawn Map Professional Online Support & Management 24/7 Uptime Guaranteed!
See our game for yourself at http://telarium.org
We hope to see you on Telarium soon!
